track_notes:
This route is a gravel forestry road and should not be attempted with low clearance vehicles. Be aware of heavy forestry vehicles and trucks.

Permission and permits to access the summit needs to be obtained from the Forestry Manager.

Contact ZS6FY for assistance in contacting the correct person.

This route can be followed to drive to MP-087. The road is a main forestry route and a high clearance 2x4 will be able to navigate it. It is a dirt road and care should be taken when it is wet or dusty.

A permit is required when using this route. Feel free to contact ZS6FY or ZS5AYC for assistance in obtaining the correct permit.

This route can be used to travel to MP-093. This is a main forestry route and should be navigable with a high clearance 2x4 vehicle.

A permit is required to use this route and access the summits. Please contact ZS6FY or ZS5AYC for assistance in obtaining the correct permits.
